---
title: Cal Smart Zesty Garlic Tofu with Fresh Greens and Olive Salad
description: Inspired by the flavours of classic Greek cuisine, this lower-calorie dish pairs juicy zesty garlic tofu with Greek-style salad and creamy yogurt sauce.

